ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND noninteractive
ENV uid 1000

RUN wget --no-check-certificate $PUPPET_URL
RUN dpkg -i $PUPPET_PACKAGE

WORKDIR puppet-alfresco



ENTRYPOINT ./install.sh
